         'class="plainlinks noexcerpt noprint asof-tag update" '
         'style="display:none;"><a class="external text" '
         'href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Transistor_count&amp;action=edit">[update]</a></sup>, '
         'the highest transistor count in a <a '
         'href="/wiki/Graphics_processing_unit" title="Graphics processing '
         'unit">graphics processing unit</a> (GPU) is <a href="/wiki/Nvidia" '
         'title="Nvidia">Nvidia</a>\'s <a '
