         'class="plainlinks noexcerpt noprint asof-tag update" '
         'style="display:none;"><a class="external text" '
         'href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Transistor_count&amp;action=edit">[update]</a></sup>, '
         'the highest transistor count in any IC chip was <a '
         'href="/wiki/Samsung_Electronics" title="Samsung '
         'Electronics">Samsung</a>\'s 1<span class="nowrap">\xa0</span><a '
         'href="/wiki/Terabyte" class="mw-redirect" title="Terabyte">TB</a> <a '
         'href="/wiki/Universal_Flash_Storage" title="Universal Flash '
